citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
Inspector arrived and called licensee. Rang doorbell and knocked on front door. Called and left messages, emailed
licensee requesting response. A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection
process at 11:45am-12:15pm on 05-DEC-2022.
End Section
